



이미지 불러오기


```python copy
from PIL import Image
img = Image.open('balloon.webp')
```


## 정보

파일 형식


```python copy
img.format
```

:::note[output]
```
'WEBP'
```

:::


크기


```python copy
img.size # 가로가 1024픽셀(점)로, 세로도 1024픽셀로 이뤄진 그림
```

:::note[output]
```
(1024, 1024)
```

:::


색상 모드


```python copy
img.mode
```

:::note[output]
```
'RGB'
```

:::


## 크기 변경


```python copy
img = img.resize((256,256))
img
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


크기를 반으로 줄이기


```python copy
w, h = img.size
```



```python copy
w // 2 # 2로 나눈 몫
```

:::note[output]
```
128
```

:::



```python copy
int(w / 2) # 나누기 후 정수로 변환해서 소수점 이하는 버림
```

:::note[output]
```
128
```

:::



```python copy
size = w // 2, h // 2
small = img.resize(size)
small
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=128x128>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::



```python copy
small.save('small.png')
```


## 변환

상하반전


```python copy
img.transpose(Image.Transpose.FLIP_TOP_BOTTOM)
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


좌우반전


```python copy
img.transpose(Image.Transpose.FLIP_LEFT_RIGHT)
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


45도 회전


```python copy
img.rotate(45)
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


색상 모드를 흑백으로


```python copy
img.convert('L')
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=L size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


## RGB 채널 분리


```python copy
red, green, blue = img.split()
red
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=L size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


빈 이미지


```python copy
empty = Image.new('L', img.size)
empty
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=L size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAQAAAAEACAAAAAB5Gfe6AAAAVElEQVR4nO3BAQEAAACAkP6v7ggKAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAGAEPAAFN9soGAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC)

:::


Red 채널을 빨간색으로 표시(Green, Blue 채널은 빈 이미지로)


```python copy
Image.merge('RGB', (red, empty, empty))
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


응용: Blue 채널도 같은 방식으로


```python copy
Image.merge('RGB', (empty, empty, blue))
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


## 필터
경계선 검출


```python copy
from PIL import ImageFilter
img1 = img.convert('L')
img2 = img1.filter(ImageFilter.FIND_EDGES)
img2
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=L size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


경계선 강조


```python copy
img3 = img2.filter(ImageFilter.EDGE_ENHANCE)
img3
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=L size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


흐리게


```python copy
img.filter(ImageFilter.BLUR)
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::


윤곽선


```python copy
img.filter(ImageFilter.CONTOUR)
```

:::note[output]
```
<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=256x256>
```

![](data:image/png;base64,)

:::
